Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the example of two youths, Dororo and Hyakkimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,this story will depict the lives of people in the chaos of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo is an orphaned child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru has had 48 parts of his body, including his limbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,stolen from him by demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But, after being raised by a doctor named Jukou,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,he leaves on a journey to slay the demons and reclaim his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Note that this film is a digest version, not the main feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:59.87,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(000,400)\pos(367.2,-15)\frz358.5}Dororo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of this young man is Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To properly acquaint you with Hyakkimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we must turn back to his origins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,O 48 devils, O demons, hear my plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I seek to rule! By any means necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend unto me your power, that I may make this country my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In return, I will reward you with whatever you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I will give you my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My child's eyes, nose, mouth, hands, feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may divide them amongst yourselves as you please!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,O 48 demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you may take from my child's body whichever 48 pieces please you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Was it born?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My end of the bargain is fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They've carved up my son as promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this country will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw that monstrosity away! It's an impediment to my rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You call him a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This boy is your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not! Now dispose of that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru... Hyakkimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:05:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have 48 demons stalking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Answer me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 48 pieces of your body missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat the 48 demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can, your body will return to that of a normal human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He said if I can slay 48 demons I can be a normal human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Save me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone come save me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was some impressive swordsmanship there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those swords you've got on your arms are especially stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With how sharp they are, I'll bet they fetch a pretty price, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Did I say something that offended you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, hurry up and beat it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha and hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided I'm gonna swipe your swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You? Take these swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not look it, but I'm the famous kid thief, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I set my eyes on something, come war or dump truck collision,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to make it mine or no one'll respect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, no good is going to come from following me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! I'm not going to back down that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The grim reaper stalks me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? Well, now I want to follow you more than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens isn't my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd ever count on you for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus begins Hyakkimaru and Dororo's strange journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No outsiders may enter this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have strict orders from Lady Bandai to that effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go on! Turn back around! - Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem? I'm just going through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This brat isn't listening! Tie them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what did we do wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:09:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the two of you bound for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going demon slaying with Bro here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no monsters in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly the kind of town I'd expect to find a monster in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this village peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose this cannot be helped then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tie them up in the well house as per usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, what's their problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no darn sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, that Bandai woman is--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hearing something from the bottom of the well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Did I let it get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I could feel that I landed a hit though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, let's try going inside the well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible this well is connected to the inside of the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah! Bro! It came out inside the mansion like you thought!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you've seen me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-Bro, it's here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon, you've shown your true colors at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not terrified of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Hyakkimaru, eagerly look forward to meeting demons like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to become fully human as soon as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-Bro, the roof is caving in!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Curse you, demon! The mansion was a fake too?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know what I am, I cannot let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try to get closer. I'll crush you under this bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-your arm? What's wrong with your arm, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The sword...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro! Your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew an arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dororo, it's my arm!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, Dororo!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my arm!
