Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:26.65,Song,,0,0,0,,The scarlet clouds shine in my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:35.59,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to live as a normal person too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:42.75,Song,,0,0,0,,This is the song of the merciless wind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:50.77,Song,,0,0,0,,When it howls, it howls with the voice of a demon
