Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:33.01,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to call someone mother too
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:40.17,Song,,0,0,0,,This is the song of the wind of harsh destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:48.19,Song,,0,0,0,,It blows onwards, vanishing across the burned plains